                        <li class="nav-header">Documentation</li>
                        <li><a href="http://numerics.mathdotnet.com/api/">API Reference (docu)</a></li>
                        <li>API Reference (new)</li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
